Package: sqlfluffr
Type: Package
Title: SQL Linter and Formatter via 'sqlfluff'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Brenden", "Smith",
      email = "brendensmithmi@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides an R interface to the Python 'sqlfluff' SQL linter and
    formatter. Lint, fix, and parse SQL queries with support for multiple
    dialects. Includes special handling for 'glue::glue_sql' syntax with
    '{var}' placeholders.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    reticulate
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    glue
Config/reticulate:
    list(packages = list(list(package = "sqlfluff")))
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
